                            <p rend="center">Would General and Complete Disarmament Require an
                                International Police Force?</p>
                            <p>The strongly predominant opinion among those in favor of general and
                                complete disarmament is that such a state of affairs would require
                                some sort of international organization with its own police
                                force.</p>
