                            <p rend="center">Support For Nuclear Disarmament</p>
                            <p>On the more specific issue of nuclear disarmament support rises to
                                overwhelming levels in the countries surveyed.</p>
                            <p>Table 3. “What about nuclear disarmament? Would you favor or not
                                favor the abolition of nuclear weapons throughout the world?”</p>
