                            <p rend="center">Is Nuclear Disarmament Possible?</p>
                            <p>The widespread sentiment in favor of nuclear disarmament is not
                                accompanied by equally general feeling that such a course is
                                possible. <pb facs="0315" n="275" xml:id="pg_275"/> While optimism
                                holds an edge it does not attain a majority level in any of the
                                countries surveyed, and except in France, is almost matched by the
                                extent of pessimistic views.</p>
