                            <p>Any pessimism, however, on the possibility of attaining nuclear
                                disarmament would appear to be tempered by a widespread feeling that
                                the countries of the world will get together before any general
                                nuclear war on some way to avoid such a happening.</p>
                            <p>Table 6. “All things considered, do you believe that a general
